m.title: Alita:Battle Angel 4
m.story: Alita, a battle cyborg, is revived by Ido, a doctor, who realises that she actually has the soul of a teenager. Alita then sets out to learn about her past and find her true identity.
m.cast: Rosa Salazar Alita Christoph Waltz (Dr. Dyson Ido) Jennifer Connelly (Chiren) Keean Johnson (Hugo) Mahershala Ali (Vector)
